And the worst-case scenario will be,

1005
01:12:02.922 --> 01:12:06.802
well, I can relate to myself. When somebody finding a position there is no

1006
01:12:06.822 --> 01:12:10.702
reason to live for, there is no hope to look forward to, it can be somebody

1007
01:12:10.742 --> 01:12:12.162
thinking even taking their own life.

1008
01:12:12.922 --> 01:12:16.602
I had that thought for myself a couple of times when I was still seeking

1009
01:12:17.402 --> 01:12:20.402
protection in country of refuge. Did that answer your question?

1010
